      "span_text": "Assembling the expressions (4.35), (4.36), (4.37) and (4.38) and taking into account of the transformation B 5, we rewrite the term I 2 in the minimal BCJ basis as follows, As always, the contribution of this term I 2 to the BCJ numerator in the minimal basis is computed by the following inner products respectively, which in practice is to pick up the coefficients of the Parke-Taylor factors in (4.39)."
